  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You set your sights on a single creature with one intent: to kill. Channeling all of your rage and predatory instincts, you unleash a devastating attack.<br />The target must make a Constitution saving throw against your Taijutsu DC. If they have 50 HP or less, they make this saving throw with disadvantage. On a failure, if the creature is under 50 HP, they are instantly torn to shreds and die. On a success, they take 10d12 Force damage that cannot be reduced, ignores resistances, and treats immunities as resistance.<br />If the creature has more than 50 HP, they take 10d12 Force damage on a failure, along with 1 rank of Lacerated and Staggered. On a success, they take half damage but no conditions. This damage cannot be reduced, ignores resistances, and treats immunities as resistance.<br />This jutsu completely ignores temporary HP, bonuses to saving throws, and any external effects that would assist in the saving throw.</p>",
